WEBVTT

00:00.579 --> 00:02.145
<i>Previously on</i>
The Big Bang Theory...

00:02.147 --> 00:04.257
Oh, look at all
that chest hair.

00:04.358 --> 00:05.390
And overbite.

00:05.392 --> 00:07.225
Of course you're a Wolowitz.

00:09.029 --> 00:11.563
Son of a bitch, he bit me.

00:11.565 --> 00:15.000
Okay, I guess I'll just go to
the emergency room to be safe.

00:15.002 --> 00:17.769
Howie, this is just
your hypochondria.

00:17.771 --> 00:20.105
When I sat on the mute button
and thought I'd gone deaf,

00:20.107 --> 00:21.940
that was my hypochondria.

