00:30.718 --> 00:34.219
We'll find another time
to tell him I'm pregnant.

00:38.158 --> 00:39.491
Morning.

00:39.493 --> 00:40.792
Morning.

00:40.794 --> 00:42.461
"We"?

00:42.463 --> 00:43.862
What is this?

00:43.864 --> 00:45.063
I don't know.

00:45.065 --> 00:46.665
Maybe it says
something on the back.

00:48.235 --> 00:51.203
"Continued on milk."

00:51.205 --> 00:53.271
If you're tricking me
into making my own breakfast,

00:53.273 --> 00:55.440
it didn't work for my mom,
and it won't work for you.

00:57.244 --> 00:58.243
"Are."

00:58.245 --> 01:00.912
"We are..."

01:00.914 --> 01:02.581
"See spoons for more."

01:03.917 --> 01:05.316
What could it be?

01:05.319 --> 01:06.651
"We are Groot"?

01:06.653 --> 01:08.320
"We are the champions"?

01:08.322 --> 01:09.988
"We are family"?

01:09.990 --> 01:11.823
"I got all my sisters with me."

01:16.163 --> 01:17.462
Are you serious?

01:17.464 --> 01:19.631
Yeah.

01:19.633 --> 01:22.934
Are you sure?

01:24.405 --> 01:26.705
Pretty positive.

01:26.707 --> 01:28.507
That's a joke, because
the pregnancy test says...

01:28.509 --> 01:30.041
Oh, my God.

01:32.846 --> 01:34.379
This is incredible.

01:34.381 --> 01:36.982
We're gonna be parents?

01:36.984 --> 01:40.452
We're gonna get
to board planes first.

01:41.588 --> 01:43.221
Finally gonna get to see

01:43.223 --> 01:46.725
what's in that family bathroom
at the mall.

01:46.727 --> 01:48.860
I know, it's crazy.

01:48.862 --> 01:50.962
It is crazy.

01:50.964 --> 01:52.264
Oh.

01:52.266 --> 01:56.001
I mean, how do you... prepare
for something like this?

01:56.003 --> 01:59.204
I'm not even sure
I've held a baby before.

01:59.206 --> 02:00.906
Oh, it's okay,
you'll figure it out.

02:00.908 --> 02:02.841
But how's this all gonna work?

02:02.843 --> 02:03.975
Do we get a nanny?

02:03.977 --> 02:05.210
I mean, can we
afford a nanny?

02:05.212 --> 02:07.012
And if we can,
we can't get a pretty one,

02:07.014 --> 02:08.979
'cause it'll wreck our marriage.

02:10.383 --> 02:13.485
We can't get an ugly one,
'cause it'll scare the kid.

02:15.355 --> 02:17.155
I-I don't know, Howie.

02:17.157 --> 02:18.623
Are we in a good
school district?

02:18.625 --> 02:19.858
You're Catholic, I'm Jewish.

02:19.860 --> 02:21.893
What religion do
we raise it?

02:21.895 --> 02:23.395
And if it's a boy,
do we get him circumcised?

02:23.397 --> 02:24.596
People say it's barbaric,

02:24.598 --> 02:27.499
but if we don't, it looks like
a pig in a blanket.

02:30.637 --> 02:33.071
Calm down, it's
gonna be okay.

02:33.073 --> 02:34.639
How's it gonna be okay?

02:34.641 --> 02:38.076
Look at me, I'm a mess.

02:38.078 --> 02:39.744
And that means this baby's
gonna half a mess.

02:39.746 --> 02:41.012
And that's even
before we screw it up

02:41.014 --> 02:43.815
with our cut-rate
moderately attractive nanny.

02:45.018 --> 02:48.653
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

02:48.655 --> 02:51.990
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

02:51.992 --> 02:53.592
♪ The Earth began to cool ♪

02:53.594 --> 02:56.161
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

02:56.163 --> 02:58.830
♪ We built the Wall ♪
♪ <i>We built the pyramids</i> ♪

02:58.832 --> 03:01.500
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

03:01.502 --> 03:03.368
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

03:03.370 --> 03:05.200
♪ <i>Bang!</i> ♪

